Login
=====

- gogo [=~maint/00login]-> unlock, unison, progs, ~maint/01update

Packages
========

- packages.rb is a wrapper around user/packages.rb, syst/packages.rb and package_handler.rb

- 01update -> $MAINTFILES/packages.rb --shell=exec update_or_check
cf AApackages for more infos

Clean-up
========

- ~maint/packages.rb --shell=exec clean
  [gitfolders -l all action 'git gc --aggressive']
- ~/script/clean_tmp #(clean old ~/tmp files)

- folders to clean up: (cf script/clean_tmp -d foo)
  ~/var/{log,run,tmp}/*
  ~/.cache/{@comp, vim, mutt_header_cache}
  $ pacaur -a -Sc #.cache/pacaur
  $ yarn cache clean #.cache/yarn
  $ npm cache verify #.cache/npm
  $ rm -rf ~/.cache/{pip, wine, winetricks}

Machines virtuelles: ~/var/spool/{VirtualBox,vagrant.d}

SaveData
========

- ~/mine/@infos/00savedata
- gitfolders -l perso action 'echo $foldername; cat $folder/.git/config' >| ~/mine/@infos/git-configs
- dofor 'ssh-keygen -lf' ~/.ssh/*.pub >| ~/mine/@infos/ssh_fingerprints
  Si besoin: ssh-keygen -lf ~/.ssh/known_hosts

Dist
====

- gitfolders -l prodist,vardist update --auto

Config
======

- ~maint/user/00update #update config files

- ~maint/user/misc/01_unisonall #(run unison.rb -s --all on computers)
- unison.rb -t common,data,booklight,book,perso,perso2
    ens,4a,imb,feanor,numenor,FleurBleue,durin
- unison.rb --sync=photos

- ~maint/user/misc/01_updateallcomptes #(update config files on computers)
- ~maint/user/misc/09_updateunison #(update unison on computers)

Crontabs
========

- Run by an @boot crontab normally, to restart services:
  ssh phare; ~/mine/config/crontab/@boot-phare
  ssh simb;  ~/mine/config/crontab/@boot-imb
- To run manually:
  ssh simb; ~/mine/config/crontab/imb-unlock.sh #crontabs include yaf backup

New
====

- ~maint/user/01new
- ~syst/new/generate

